  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK771">
<l>eṉṉaimuṉ ṉillaṉmiṉ ṟevvir palareṉṉai</l>
<l>muṉṉiṉṟu kaṉṉiṉ ṟavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my foes, stand not before my leader; (for) many are those who did so but afterwards stood (in the shape of) statues.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
